snippet.textDisplay: Loved this!! I work at kfc so clear things up, the vegan burgers are cooked in the same oven as other non-vegan products such as mash and bacon. However, we have procedures where the vegan fillets are stored above any chicken produce (to avoid crumbs falling into them) and the vegan fillets are only stored with non-vegan items and corn is no longer sold with butter so is vegan. It’s vegan just depends how strict you are :) Hope this helps, loving the content atm x
